{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on the role of <strong>BEAR</strong>, a veteran of the elite <strong>NAVY BEARS</strong> unit in <strong>ONE BEAR ARMY</strong> \u2013 a 2.5D action-adventure game in which you will face the evil <i>Professor Rat</i> and his army. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ONE HERO, ONE MISSION: SAVE THE WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646480/extras/Gif3.gif?t=1733204439\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You once again step into the front lines to defeat the plans of <i>Professor Rat</i>. You are the only one who can achieve this goal - you're not just a soldier, you are the last line of defense against the impending chaos - you're the <strong>ONE BEAR ARMY</strong>. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CHOOSE YOUR STRATEGY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646480/extras/Gif2.gif?t=1733204439\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore dynamic environments, adapting your approach as you navigate the storyline. Some missions demand a silent touch, requiring you to slip through the shadows unnoticed. Others call for a more explosive resolution, involving the all of your <strong>BEAR</strong>-sized arsenal.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MASTER EVERY STEP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646480/extras/Gif4.gif?t=1733204439\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Move with precision\u2014whether it's wall jumping, swinging across ropes, or leaping over pits. Every move matters in your mission.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SAVE THE WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646480/extras/Gif1.gif?t=1733204439\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ONE BEAR ARMY</strong> blends storytelling with action, inviting you to uncover the mysteries behind <i>Professor Rat</i> sinister plot. The world\u2019s fate is in your hands. Are you ready to face every challenge and become the hero we need?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646480/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733204439","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646480/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733204439","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646480/06ab084e6eda636cce19ade4faa5b10b5f1a4305/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733204439","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646480/06ab084e6eda636cce19ade4faa5b10b5f1a4305/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733204439","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2783000,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h1>JOIN THE NAVY BEARS!</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WISHLIST &amp; FOLLOW:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Support us by adding to your wishlist and stay notified about all updates!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DISCORD CHANNEL:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join our Discord channel to stay updated or share your thoughts on the game!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on the role of <strong>BEAR</strong>, a veteran of the elite <strong>NAVY BEARS</strong> unit in <strong>ONE BEAR ARMY</strong> \u2013 a 2.5D action-adventure game in which you will face the evil <i>Professor Rat</i> and his army. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ONE HERO, ONE MISSION: SAVE THE WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.stea